{"tid":313282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港醫生被當「水魚」 跨境告台女網友欺詐","createTime":"2017-07-08T08:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T12:16:56.000Z","uid":13468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c7a18c5118e43637519dc7c42f1a99b9adca922","tid":313282,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"台灣一名廖姓單親媽媽（37歲），4年前透過網絡遊戲認識住在香港的葉姓醫生，因缺錢花用將葉男當成「水魚」，先謊報年齡僅26歲，父親早逝、母親改嫁身世可憐，後來又以駕駛電單車撞傷人、家人生病住院、在宏達電上班弄壞機器等不同藉口，向葉男詐騙118萬新台幣（下同‧約31萬港元）。廖女得手後避不見面，葉男察覺受騙跨海提告，高雄地檢署近日依詐欺罪嫌將廖女起訴。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書透露，廖女於2013年透過手機線上遊戲「TERA」，以化名「小蛋」認識住在香港的葉姓醫生，雙方認識之後即以LINE互相聯絡。廖女在閒聊時隱匿自己單親育有一子，反而佯稱自己未婚，在宏達電上班，父親早逝、母親改嫁，還罹患重肌無力症等，博得葉男同情。<br />\n<br />\n同年6月，廖女開始以不同藉口向葉男騙財，先後謊稱「車輛遺失，要清償貸款給保險公司」、「過馬路不慎害機車騎士跌倒要賠償」、「弟弟女友懷孕了，急著結婚但沒錢」、「弟媳早產住院沒錢辦出院手續」、「上班害公司被退貨還弄壞機器」等，葉男信以為真，一年多內先後匯款1萬至9萬港元不等，合計匯了30多萬元。<br />\n<br />\n後因廖女避不見面，葉男起疑，又發現她先前提供的是假的身份證號碼才驚悉受騙，憤而持兩人LINE對話紀錄等證據提告。廖女在檢方偵查時承認對葉男謊報年齡捏造身世，及以各種藉口向葉男「借款」，但檢察官認為其行為已構成欺詐取財，依法提起公訴。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56928125&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56928125%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170707&d=D7v3H1Tz4pV97MhcSR622E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d409edea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56928125%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170707&h=188d1ba4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56928125&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170707</a>"},{"pid":"2fd0d38f55ef9cdc86ed63eae5407b20b6631665","tid":313282,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"醫生都要比女人撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb073a32a770b459a7b47a8041aa50943cd601f","tid":313282,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a500dbfe120bde2aa3bed49a57ef08f82e9232e9","tid":313282,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9a8244c21738845fd71ee0e052b3c5e20349826","tid":313282,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"醫生咁得閒打online game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9933f60d68f6bc2d0efa553bf627352f8dd01da8","tid":313282,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生咁得閒打online game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把啦"},{"pid":"87c69a03a80a95db51ee47ee11cf98fa21421247","tid":313282,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"係女人都好啲 強國呢類案9成女網友其實係男人"},{"pid":"bb785f6c4a5ee3b39155cac114b100612003d9ab","tid":313282,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d39e64e401697306e6008c276e60edb61e02047c","tid":313282,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"由細到大努力讀書做醫生既 毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf145bc19407dc7dc722fffccf98d72eeb1dce7d","tid":313282,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"為食女立志讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}